name: Fancade - Nonsense
description:
It's Nonsense Time!

Nonsense is a Fancade drag-n-drop puzzle game where you rearrange tiles within the rules:

  • Two or more tiles with different texture should not be positioned near each other
  • Two or more tiles with the same texture may or may not be positioned near each other
  • Same rules also applied to mini tiles and locked tiles

Hope you enjoy this nonsensical puzzle!
